       <div class="col-md-12">
        <h2>
         Safety News &amp; Tips
        </h2>
       </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
       <div class="col-md-12 news">
        <p class="tag">
         News
        </p>
        <h3>
         UCAIR
        </h3>
        <p>
         Environmental Health and Safety (EHS) and the Office of Research Safety (ORS) recently launched the University of Chicago Accident &amp; Incident Reporting system (UCAIR), which enables anyone to submit accident and incident reports to allow for immediate notification to the appropriate safety office. It helps the University’s safety-related departments identify accident or incident trends, determine causes, and proactively eliminate hazardous conditions by evaluating reports submitted into the system. For additional information about the accident and injury reporting process visit the UCAIR website http://ucair.uchicago.edu/.
        </p>
       </div>
      </div>
